commit_message: Updating version number to match latest tagged version.
Newer versions of perl don't allow foreach...qw().  Corrected to foreach...(qw()).
Added bam file index to distribution.
Formatting correction in DOCUMENTATION, and added citation to "README" files.

Adding filter field to VCF (MPG score >= 10 and score/coverage ratio >= 0.5).  Also
improving memory management for large runs.
Adding test reference file for the tests.
Getting rid of large bam files.
